<plot>Joe McDoakes (George O'Hanlon) receives a wire telling him he will inherit his grandmother's million dollar estate if he reaches her before she dies. He rushes to her home where he is met by some weird relatives (all played by O'Hanlon) and a weird lawyer (Philip Van Zandt). Grandmother informs him the wire is a gag but that the others don't know and will probably try to murder him for the inheritance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503864</url></doc>
